module count_slow(
    input clk,
    input slowena,
    input reset,
    output reg [3:0] q
);

always @(posedge clk) begin
    if (reset) begin
        q <= 4'b0000;
    end else if (slowena) begin
        case(q)
            4'b0100: q <= 4'b0000;
            default: q <= q + 1;
        endcase
    end
end

endmodule
